results.title: Valentine's in shades of Pink! Cupid too, Your set, your choice of charms
results.description:
This listing is for Valentines in silver tone charms and 3 shades of pink: lite pink, hot pink, and grey pink. It's quite subtle, and unusual!  My wine rings last for years because they are made with stainless steel memory wire that wraps around the wine glass stem like a bracelet. Beads all the way around!

Occasionally if the stems on your glasses is wide, or someone rips it off the glass to put the glasses in the dishwasher, they may get stretched out - so just wind them up tight and squeeze them back into round. Mine stay on the glass right into the dishwasher if i leave them on for a season, i.e. Thanksgiving.
